      "bookmarkId": "35361156_48_2855-2909",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "2855-2909",
      "markText": "仿佛生命最重要的事情就是等待，仿佛生命的意义将出现于等待的间歇，或者抽象的未来。除了忍耐，别无其他实现之途。",
      "totalCount": 4260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2909",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2855&rangeEnd=2909"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_54_11062-11124",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "11062-11124",
      "markText": "存在是最重要的。世界是一个荒谬的地方，充满了矛盾和存在的困惑。但只有拥有目标的人才可能找到意义。我们必须想象，鳗鱼是幸运的。",
      "totalCount": 3504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=11062&rangeEnd=11124",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=11062&rangeEnd=11124"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_49_1349-1390",
      "chapterUid": 49,
      "range": "1349-1390",
      "markText": "我们无法知道任何事情，但我们选择相信，有时候我们必须这么相信。钓鱼常常就在于相信。",
      "totalCount": 3330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=49&rangeStart=1349&rangeEnd=1390",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=49&rangeStart=1349&rangeEnd=1390"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_57_1603-1680",
      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "1603-1680",
      "markText": "说到底，人需要成为某种具有延续性的东西的一部分，才能感觉自己属于某种在其存在之前就已开始、在其消失之后仍将继续存在的永恒。人需要成为某种更大事物的一部分。",
      "totalCount": 2992,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=1603&rangeEnd=1680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=1603&rangeEnd=1680"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_48_542-588",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "542-588",
      "markText": "马尾藻海就像梦境一样：你无法确切地说出你何时进入，又何时走出它。你只知道，自己曾经去过那里。",
      "totalCount": 2640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=588",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=542&rangeEnd=588"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_48_2080-2177",
      "chapterUid": 48,
      "range": "2080-2177",
      "markText": "外部的环境似乎无法阻挡它们，别无选择时，它们甚至可以游走在陆地上，游过湿润的灌木丛和草地，坚持若干小时，直到抵达新的水域。如此看来，鳗鱼是一种超越了鱼类自身条件的鱼。它们可能都意识不到自己是鱼。",
      "totalCount": 2016,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2080&rangeEnd=2177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=48&rangeStart=2080&rangeEnd=2177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_62_5798-5874",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "5798-5874",
      "markText": "也许，很简单，每个鳗鱼个体不仅能力不同，抵达目的地的手段和方法也不同。也许它们回归自己出生地的目标是一致的，但没有一条鳗鱼的旅途跟其他鳗鱼是完全一样的。",
      "totalCount": 1980,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5798&rangeEnd=5874",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=5798&rangeEnd=5874"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_51_3985-4035",
      "chapterUid": 51,
      "range": "3985-4035",
      "markText": "每当我们抓住一条鳗鱼的时候，我都会凝视它的眼睛，想一瞥它曾经看见的那些东西。可它从不曾与我四目相接。",
      "totalCount": 1870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=51&rangeStart=3985&rangeEnd=4035",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=51&rangeStart=3985&rangeEnd=4035"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35361156_61_2317-2392",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "2317-2392",
      "markText": "爸爸和妈妈的这场旅行自然不是被事先设定好的，但这也并非偶然。强大的力量一直在发挥作用。他们就是海流中的柳叶鳗。他们游过了一整片海洋，但其实根本没有动。",
      "totalCount": 1818,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35361156&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=2317&rangeEnd=2392",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/380329d0721b918438013b4?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=2317&rangeEnd=2392"
    },
    {
